profile.name: Mikeal Rogers
profile.headline: Senior Software Engineer at Oracle Corporation | Open Source Enthusiast
profile.summary: Highly motivated and experienced software engineer with a passion for open-source development. Proficient in multiple programming languages, including JavaScript, Shell, Python, and HTML. Proven track record of contributing to successful projects and collaborating with cross-functional teams.
